                            <li><strong>License Suspension:</strong> 30 days hard suspension, followed by 150 days restricted</li>
                            <li><strong>Community Service:</strong> Up to 360 hours</li>
                            <li><strong>Points:</strong> 6 points on your driving record</li>
                            <li><strong>Criminal Record:</strong> Misdemeanor conviction that shows on background checks</li>
                            <li><strong>Probation:</strong> Typically 1-2 years with alcohol testing and reporting requirements</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h3>Second Offense OWI (within 7 years)</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Jail:</strong> 5 days to 1 year (jail time is <em>mandatory</em>, but may be suspended if you complete a treatment court program such as sobriety court or drug court)</li>
