                            <li><strong>Vehicle Immobilization or Forfeiture:</strong> 90-180 days or permanent seizure</li>
                            <li><strong>Ignition Interlock:</strong> Required for license restoration</li>
                            <li><strong>Probation:</strong> Often includes substance abuse treatment, frequent testing</li>
