                            <li><strong>Fines:</strong> Up to $700</li>
                            <li><strong>License Suspension:</strong> 1 year hard suspension (no restricted license)</li>
                            <li><strong>Ignition Interlock:</strong> Required for restricted license after 45 days</li>
                            <li><strong>Alcohol Monitoring:</strong> Court-ordered sobriety monitoring device</li>
